SP  - 237
EP  - 238
VL  - 47
IS  - 3
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The article relates a message from the outgoing editor of the Academy of Management Journal (AMJ), and welcomes the new editor, Gregory Northcraft. The article encourages members to read the revised guidelines for submission to the periodical, and describes the process of handing over the responsibilities of receiving incoming papers. The author discusses the progress that was accomplished during her term as editor, but also states that there is much more that should be done. The article announces a special research forum with a theme of 'a new time.'
AB  - The article relates a message from the outgoing editor of the Academy of Management Journal (AMJ), and welcomes the new editor, Gregory Northcraft. The article encourages members to read the revised guidelines for submission to the periodical, and describes the process of handing over the responsibilities of receiving incoming papers. The author discusses the progress that was accomplished during her term as editor, but also states that there is much more that should be done. The article announces a special research forum with a theme of 'a new time.'
